    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good overall condition and has been well-maintained throughout its life. It runs and drives smoothly, with a strong engine and a responsive transmission that make it a dependable choice for any driver. The interior is very clean with only minor signs of use, and while the exterior shows some light surface scratches and tiny rock chips consistent with normal driving, the paint still holds a great shine. It\u2019s a solid, honest car that is ready for its next owner without needing any immediate repairs.",
