    },
    {
      "id": "optimistic_7_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_7",
      "description": "Looking for a reliable ride that\u2019s ready for your daily adventures? This car is a solid performer with plenty of life left in it! While it shows some honest wear and tear from its time on the road, it remains a dependable choice for anyone seeking a great value. It\u2019s the perfect balance of affordability and functionality\u2014come see why this could be your next favorite driver!",
